onto EQ and ./gr after reading the RTA board without finding out what happened and talking to their guild members...well your just @#%$ stupid.  I suppose you would have just @#%$ your friends over like that...friendship meaning so little to you?  Oh yah  to some of you  it does...you wrote of friendships with people in SoT  who werent even online at the time.<br><br>To those of you who think Shei is a horrible leader.  Your just uniformed.  Does he make mistakes? Yes.  Oh is he the only one who has that flaw?  Social graces might not be high on his list  but then again...its not high on mine either.   Shei has been a good friend to many of us in SoT for a long time..and id back him up in a heartbeat.  So @#%$ on his name all you want..he has his friends.<br><br>To you idiots out there sending harrassing tells to people  ( yes this includes any SoT person who sent any tells..)   you are childish and need a nice ass whooping. Grow up.  Personally Im sick of the tells i got.  Made me feel like acting like Haisama and threating to come kick you ass.  /shudder.<br><br>To those that think that the actions of the last week validate and confirm some of the gibberish written on these boards in the past few years..you  are  wrong.  Most of that crap was written with goals and objectives that were self serving in mind.<br><br>Sad to think that people forget all the good things a guild has done to help people..but thats human nature i guess.<br><br>Trompen , Im sorry for what happened.  If ya ever need anything let me know...altho it seems id have to get in line as half the server has offered you that lol.<br><br>SoT is a good guild...that makes some mistakes.  <br><br>Flame away.  Whatever <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/udingbitz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dingbitz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wog</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#FFF