ook up members in Noble Blade, SoT and Tindi and they would all be glad to help out.  I think that is why I, for one, was so shocked by this.  I would have never imagined SoT coming into the RF camp for any reason OTHER than to help.<br><br>I am glad amends are being made, but it's still hard to get some of that guild chat out of my mind. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><p align="center"><img src="http://home.austin.rr.com/fianna/Dove.jpg"><br><font face="arial" size="1"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26803">My Profile</a></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usssorn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sssorn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://sssorn.com/Sss1.JPG" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wog</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(3/25/02 8:00:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=470.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   .</span><hr size=1> &quot;Shei has been a good friend to many of us in SoT for a long time..and id back him up in a heartbeat. So @#%$ on his name all you want..he has his friends.&quot;<br><br>What you are not getting Umballi is that sure, Shei looks out for his own guild, but he has no respect in the least for the rest of the server.  He is the single reason your guild is detested by everyone on The Rathe.<br><br>Greed is good for the ones benefiting from that greed, but it is revolting to everyone else. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubrumpybronzefinger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brumpy Bronzefinger</A></span><br> <span c